OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading this evening, leaving a dry and
OL,7,Fclear night to develop across much of
OL,8,Fthe region. However, showers may
OL,9,Fcontinue overnight in western
OL,10,FCornwall. Turning chilly in the
OL,11,Fcountryside.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at times
OL,14,Facross southern coasts with some
OL,15,Ffurther showery rain towards Cornwall
OL,16,Fand later into Devon. Largely dry with
OL,17,Fsunny spells elsewhere, and feeling
OL,18,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
