OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain clearing Sunday with a dry but
OL,7,Fcooler afternoon following. Largely
OL,8,Fdry but cool on Monday and Tuesday,
OL,9,Fwith some bright spells, but rain
OL,10,Fpossible overnight into Tuesday.
